single-point analysis (Sec 9) with five new, more capable sections:

D  Single Location Analysis — 4-panel figure per site.
E  Parameter Sensitivity Analysis — sweeps one parameter at a time.
F  Material Property Profiles (article figure).
G  Sensitivity Tornado Chart (article figure).
H  Apollo HFE Residual Analysis (article figure).

